ign=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.nuclearspace.com/ezboard/images/posticons/fry1.gif" align=absmiddle>  Re: Dont be so fast to judge the result.</span><hr size=1> As an observation...<br>
<br>
Nuclear power and propulsion is likely to only be used on a craft WAY larger than current spaceships.  It would likely be impractical to even attempt an atmospheric launch based upon flight characteristics of the ship.<br>
<br>
Therefore, the question of nuclear launches from atmosphere will likely never matter. =)<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
